&lt;div data-page-id=&quot;Nttid6qB9oltGwxgP5wcpPZ4nyf&quot; data-lark-html-role=&quot;root&quot; data-docx-has-block-data=&quot;false&quot;&gt;
&lt;h4 class=&quot;heading-4 ace-line old-record-id-Jm7cdynzwoUf7WxIju4cVYPCn0c&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Role Overview:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;ace-line ace-line old-record-id-S34Wdkck2o3WCGxGnbNc1tX7nxd&quot;&gt;We are seeking a talented Product Designer to join our team in Shenzhen, China. This role focuses on creating innovative and intuitive user experiences across our product portfolio, including consumer-facing imaging tools for lifestyle scenarios and professional imaging applications for productivity scenarios. The ideal candidate will possess strong aesthetic judgment, trend awareness, and the ability to contribute to evolving design systems.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;ace-line ace-line old-record-id-T10vd02xHoHEB1xUPrOcw4TcnLh&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h4 class=&quot;heading-4 ace-line old-record-id-ZlXhd2CUaoc6KZxzMVKcDNv1nah&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key Responsibilities:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ol class=&quot;list-number1&quot;&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Is7SdZOYsoAGONxyjrGcYS6en8f&quot; data-list=&quot;number&quot;&gt;
&lt;div&gt;Design Excellence:&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;ace-line text-indent ace-line old-record-id-PtO3dsKAfoXnkGxF6fdcq8TpnIf&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;-Create sophisticated, trend-setting visual designs that balance aesthetics with functionality&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;ace-line text-indent ace-line old-record-id-I958dCQNgoSwQyxDbQZcKg33nOe&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;-Contribute to the development and maintenance of comprehensive design systems&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;ace-line text-indent ace-line old-record-id-Ip2IdeAWroVYWLxNHIlcCCNMnWg&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;-Implement and follow design principles and patterns that enhance product consistency&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;ace-line text-indent ace-line old-record-id-QRODdNZSUo6vHLxu9R2cpLaBnXb&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;-Deliver high-quality design work from concept to final implementation&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;ol class=&quot;list-number1&quot;&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;ace-line ace-line old-record-id-VSDzdod9KoBT5TxZyGfcmbzSntb&quot; data-list=&quot;number&quot;&gt;
&lt;div&gt;User Experience &amp;amp; Research:&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;ace-line text-indent ace-line old-record-id-S3dNdUscIosA6ExRGSCcLq8dnSg&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;-Participate in user research to understand user behaviors, needs, and motivations&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;ace-line text-indent ace-line old-record-id-K6mnddAr4oOiNgxTsGucYJgZnuc&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;-Create user flows, wireframes, and high-fidelity prototypes&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;ace-line text-indent ace-line old-record-id-KWlEdBdUUoaWapxDrFZcB3bWnSd&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;-Conduct usability testing and incorporate feedback into design solutions&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;ace-line text-indent ace-line old-record-id-V8ZudQVtHoDWdFx4X6bcJTqlnQj&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;-Analyze user feedback to inform design decisions&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;ol class=&quot;list-number1&quot;&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;ace-line ace-line old-record-id-WE2SdIEpboWqFkxe9wqcvgMQnKc&quot; data-list=&quot;number&quot;&gt;
&lt;div&gt;Cross-functional Collaboration:&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;ace-line text-indent ace-line old-record-id-IXf3djX8souaRUxqbfqcDyjHnHh&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;-Work closely with product managers, engineers, and researchers&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;ace-li

&lt;p&gt;Influencer Outreach &amp;amp; Collaboration&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;Responsibilities:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;1. Identify and research relevant influencers in your target markets.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;2. Develop and manage influencer outreach campaigns.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;3. Negotiate and secure collaborations with influencers, including affiliate programs and permission to use their image for marketing purposes.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;4. Research &amp;amp; Insights: Monitor local trending topics and social media conversations. Provide insights and recommendations to designers and the marketing team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Qualifications:&lt;br&gt;1. 2+ years of experience in Influencer Outreach &amp;amp; Collaboration or related field&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;2. Excellent communication，result-driven and interpersonal skills.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;3. Strong understanding of influencer marketing strategies and platforms.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;4. Experience with research and competitor analysis.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;5. Creativity and ability to build relationships with influencers.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div data-page-id=&quot;LyjndPS8loURp0xCB7bcmdt9nEc&quot; data-lark-html-role=&quot;root&quot; data-docx-has-block-data=&quot;false&quot;&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;ace-line ace-line old-record-id-QiUEd3r7WoMAjVxLpc9cF20DnWc&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Role overview：&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;ace-line ace-line old-record-id-GZyndJuWnoS7AJxWGgXc6Dm4nTd&quot;&gt;You will be responsible for the visual design of Pixocial’s flagship products, such as&lt;span class=&quot;Apple-converted-space&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;AirBrush&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;Apple-converted-space&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;and&lt;span class=&quot;Apple-converted-space&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;BeautyPlus&lt;/strong&gt;,&lt;span class=&quot;Apple-converted-space&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;serving tens of millions of MAUs. Your work includes executing brand designs independently, developing brand VI systems and guidelines collaboratively with the team, and sharing insights on the US market’s aesthetic/visual trends and innovations. This role requires a global perspective, with a focus on the US market, and a deep understanding of local users&#39; aesthetic preferences and cultural backgrounds to deliver designs that resonate with diverse audiences.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;
&lt;div data-page-id=&quot;LyjndPS8loURp0xCB7bcmdt9nEc&quot; data-lark-html-role=&quot;root&quot; data-docx-has-block-data=&quot;false&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div data-page-id=&quot;LyjndPS8loURp0xCB7bcmdt9nEc&quot; data-lark-html-role=&quot;root&quot; data-docx-has-block-data=&quot;false&quot;&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;ace-line ace-line old-record-id-EutadkFvoo5CQmxUnTtcHWPWnif&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key Responsibilities:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;list-bullet1&quot;&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Ofy7dHMqCoTjGkxbAMRcDVZenVh&quot; data-list=&quot;bullet&quot;&gt;
&lt;div&gt;Plan and execute brand designs and VI systems and guidelines, aligning with product strategies and delivering creative, visually appealing outputs for existing and new products.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;ace-line ace-line old-record-id-GUi6dMODJoV5BHxBSiOcpYzsnDb&quot; data-list=&quot;bullet&quot;&gt;
&lt;div&gt;Share insights on US design/visual trends to enhance global brand perception and the team’s understanding of international aesthetics, while creating visuals aligned with global market preferences.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;ace-line ace-line old-record-id-LNMgdKXLnoBxEoxoSZxcqeuSnxd&quot; data-list=&quot;bullet&quot;&gt;
&lt;div&gt;Conduct research on diverse aesthetic preferences in international markets, considering local trends, cultural backgrounds, and behaviors to inform design strategies.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;ace-line ace-line old-record-id-GLlidVr2loxMBvxupOVc3vsTn1W&quot; data-list=&quot;bullet&quot;&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Collaborate closely with product teams to create feasible designs that align with business goals.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Vea7dCqB7o7yX6xzcwJc5gbXnyb&quot; data-list=&quot;bullet&quot;&gt;
&lt;div&gt;Proactively communicate with other designers/teams to ensure design quality and enhance brand awareness.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;ace-line ace-line old-record-id-MIFpdOTcvoebeRxHzGOcvi8tn8b&quot; data-list=&quot;bullet&quot;&gt;
&lt;div&gt;Stay up to date with design trends, actively participating in creative brainstorming sessions and globalization project planning.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;ace-line ace-line old-record-id-Wwi9dTfP7o3mMsxJ7eEc1ldJnme&quot; data-list=&quot;bullet&quot;&gt;
&lt;div&gt;Independently manage end-to-end brand design projects, focusing on detail and precision.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
